{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be minimalist and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evergreen Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #A02020; /* Red */\n            --secondary-color: #D8BFD8; /* Thistle - a softer, less contrasting color */\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 10px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 10px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            padding: 50px 20px;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            margin-top: 20px;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: #8B0000; /* Darker red */\n        }\n\n        .about, .collection {\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n        }\n\n        .about h3, .collection h3 {\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            font-size: 1.8em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .about p, .collection p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: var(--text-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--background-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Evergreen Threads</h1>\n    </header>\n\n    <nav>\n        <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n        <a href=\"#collection\">Our Collection</a>\n        <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n    </nav>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section class=\"hero\">\n            <h2>Style That Cares</h2>\n            <p>Discover conscious fashion crafted with sustainable materials and ethical practices. Look good, feel good, do good.</p>\n            <a href=\"#collection\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Now</a>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"about\" class=\"about\">\n            <h3>Our Commitment</h3>\n            <p>At Evergreen Threads, we believe fashion should not cost the Earth. We are dedicated to creating timeless pieces using eco-friendly fabrics like organic cotton, recycled polyester, and linen. Our production processes prioritize minimal waste and fair labor, ensuring transparency from fiber to finished garment.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"collection\" class=\"collection\">\n            <h3>Explore Our Latest Collection</h3>\n            <p>Timeless designs, made to last. Our collection features versatile essentials for the modern, conscious consumer. From organic cotton tees to elegant linen dresses, find pieces that blend style and sustainability seamlessly.</p>\n            <p><em>(Imagine product images and descriptions here)</em></p>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n        <p>Contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\" style=\"color: var(--secondary-color); text-decoration: underline;\">info@evergreenthreads.com</a></p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}